name: Runner's Blueprint Couch to 5K
description: Popular 8 week "Couch to 5K" plan from Runner's Blueprint.

workouts.title: Session I, Workout Time: 20 min
workouts.description: A 5-min brisk walk followed by a 30-sec jog and a 90-sec walk. Repeat 5 times.

workouts.title: Session II, Workout Time: 20 min
workouts.description: A 5-min brisk walk followed by a 30-sec jog, and one-min walk. Repeat 6 times.

workouts.description: A 5-min brisk walk followed by a 30-sec jog and a one-min walk. Repeat 8 times.
